{"type": "article", "id": 20409, "title": "这个英国少年，用乐高积木讲述人类历史｜好奇心人类学", "description": "这里是关于他的作品的图片集锦。", "date": "2016-01-08T15:04:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8377, "name": "积木"}, {"id": 773, "name": "历史"}, {"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 21767, "name": "Morgan Spence"}], "category": 5, "column": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 199, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606081246217mRFAlLEV5BjUH4C.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t来自英国蓝夫鲁郡的 16 岁男孩 Morgan Spence 花了一个月的时间拍摄了一段趣味<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zqlG26hESiA\" target=\"_blank\">视频</a>。他使用乐高积木，搭建了诸多历史场景，并以定格动画的形式呈现。视频中的画面，从 15000 年前的史前岩画到柏林墙倒塌，生动地展现了人类历史。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124613GU9xEA1kbnNqHmlO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081246137xfe28grzZpwJX65.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124614lm8iP2yhxGcaA70Q.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124614IkizTf89q2VohYON.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124615q58zU0DsoE4jd7pN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124615sahYjyH4lZFSMKOf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081246162lWwRm0qt9ToCxg3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124616nwuzVGgYRKkyBWId.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124617Zpc0rnHtfjWdvLYF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124617XaYCjlA5Ts6wUg2J.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124618KQ1xXb5YdWtcuwoC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606081246184fX2JUZyg0bamhO9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124618hCkcsWlyVSPK8YOB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在此之前，他已经是个小有名气的“电影人”了：2014 年，他花了仅仅两个星期就制作出了一段以电影为主题的乐高积木<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kbB61_urAlg\" target=\"_blank\">视频</a>，其中囊括了来自 13 部电影中的场景或者是海报，还原度还真的挺高的：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124619lHj0gnGF39awhQPi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124620NPcgdTbRL81jwHYi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124620CVJbUmsiNz9dIHAl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t你还可以在他的<a href=\"http://morgspennyproductions.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">个人主页</a>上看到更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}